column2: SELECT    m.id, o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2, o.z AS redshift, o.veldispz AS velocity into Group_#kpc_w_redshift FROM MyDB.og_redmapper_sample AS m    CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq( m.ra, m.dec, m.dist) AS n   JOIN SpecObj AS o ON n.objid=o.bestobjid   Join PhotoObj as p on p.objID = o.bestobjid WHERE p.petroMag_i < m.imag AND p.type = # order by m.id
